Package gov.nist.timestampingauthority

Class ClientEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nist.timestampingauthority.ClientEvent
  • public class ClientEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Data class representing unique client event. It is created each time with a unique id when the new event comes in.

                   int port,
                   java.net.InetAddress address)
        Create new client event. Stores NTP message, time received, port and address from which it was received. New unique ID is generated each time.
        Parameters:
        message - client NTP message
        receiveTime - server time when the event was received
        port - port from which the event was received
        address - address from which the event was received
